name: fabric-client
readme:
## Hyperledger Fabric Client for Node.js [![NPM](https://nodei.co/npm/fabric-client.svg?downloads=true&downloadRank=true&stars=true)](https://nodei.co/npm/fabric-fabric-client/) SDK for writing node.js applications to interact with [Hyperledger Fabric](http://hyperledger-fabric.readthedocs.io/en/latest/). This package encapsulates the APIs to interact with Peers and Orderers of the Fabric network to install and instantiate chaincodes, send transaction invocations and perform chaincode queries. A separate package is provided, `fabric-ca-client`, to interact with the fabric-ca to manage user certificates. For application developer documentations, please visit [https://fabric-sdk-node.github.io/](https://fabric-sdk-node.github.io/)
